dc_title_s: Meiji kaisei Tōkyō zenzu fusai Yokohama shigaizu; Miyagi Keiten.
dc_description_s: Mounted cover title. Copperplate print. In Japanese. Oriented with north to the upper right. 6 sheets joined. Relief shown by hachures. Includes address chart of banks, inset of Yokohama and legend. 1 map: col.; 83 x 96 cm., folded in cover 19 x 13 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
